{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1167,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":2474,"text":"I have only got 18 minutes"},{"time":3983,"text":"to explain something \nthat lasts for hours and days,"},{"time":6832,"text":"so I'd better get started."},{"time":9102,"text":"Let's start with a clip\nfrom Al Jazeera's Listening Post."}]},{"cues":[{"time":14649,"text":"Richard Gizbert: Norway is a country that \ngets relatively little media coverage."},{"time":18496,"text":"Even the elections this past week\npassed without much drama."},{"time":21487,"text":"And that's the Norwegian\nmedia in a nutshell:"},{"time":24145,"text":"not much drama."},{"time":25622,"text":"A few years back,"},{"time":26959,"text":"Norway's public TV channel NRK"},{"time":29416,"text":"decided to broadcast live coverage\nof a seven-hour train ride --"},{"time":33593,"text":"seven hours of simple footage,"},{"time":35894,"text":"a train rolling down the tracks."},{"time":38123,"text":"Norwegians, more than a million of them\naccording to the ratings, loved it."},{"time":41985,"text":"A new kind of reality TV show was born,"},{"time":44901,"text":"and it goes against all the rules\nof TV engagement."},{"time":48036,"text":"There is no story line, no script,"},{"time":50476,"text":"no drama, no climax,"},{"time":52519,"text":"and it's called Slow TV."},{"time":54443,"text":"For the past two months,"},{"time":55915,"text":"Norwegians have been watching \na cruise ship's journey up the coast,"},{"time":59507,"text":"and there's a lot of fog on that coast."},{"time":61566,"text":"Executives at Norway's\nNational Broadcasting Service"},{"time":64639,"text":"are now considering broadcasting\na night of knitting nationwide."},{"time":68729,"text":"On the surface, it sounds boring,"},{"time":71210,"text":"because it is,"},{"time":72510,"text":"but something about this TV experiment"},{"time":74600,"text":"has gripped Norwegians."},{"time":76458,"text":"So we sent the Listening Post's\nMarcela Pizarro to Oslo"},{"time":79615,"text":"to find out what it is,\nbut first a warning:"},{"time":82146,"text":"Viewers may find some of the images\nin the following report disappointing."},{"time":86649,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":88034,"text":"Thomas Hellum: And then follows\nan eight-minute story on Al Jazeera"},{"time":91550,"text":"about some strange\nTV programs in little Norway."},{"time":94876,"text":"Al Jazeera. CNN. How did we get there?"},{"time":97934,"text":"We have to go back to 2009,"},{"time":99954,"text":"when one of my colleagues\ngot a great idea."},{"time":101953,"text":"Where do you get your ideas?"},{"time":103756,"text":"In the lunchroom."},{"time":105737,"text":"So he said, why don't we make\na radio program"},{"time":108714,"text":"marking the day of the German invasion\nof Norway in 1940."},{"time":112299,"text":"We tell the story at the exact time\nduring the night."},{"time":116343,"text":"Wow. Brilliant idea, except"},{"time":118507,"text":"this was just a couple of weeks\nbefore the invasion day."},{"time":121410,"text":"So we sat in our lunchroom and discussed"},{"time":123755,"text":"what other stories\ncan you tell as they evolve?"},{"time":127963,"text":"What other things take a really long time?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":132421,"text":"So one of us came up with a train."},{"time":134737,"text":"The Bergen Railway had its \n100-year anniversary that year"},{"time":138729,"text":"It goes from western Norway\nto eastern Norway,"},{"time":141424,"text":"and it takes exactly the same time\nas it did 40 years ago,"},{"time":145587,"text":"over seven hours. (Laughter)"},{"time":148785,"text":"So we caught our commissioning editors \nin Oslo, and we said,"},{"time":151771,"text":"we want to make a documentary\nabout the Bergen Railway,"},{"time":154758,"text":"and we want to make it in full length,"},{"time":156710,"text":"and the answer was,"},{"time":158064,"text":"\"Yes, but how long will the program be?\""},{"time":159999,"text":"\"Oh,\" we said, \"full length.\""},{"time":161857,"text":"\"Yes, but we mean the program.\""},{"time":163349,"text":"And back and forth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":165456,"text":"Luckily for us, they met us with laughter,\nvery, very good laughter,"},{"time":170943,"text":"so one bright day in September,"},{"time":173629,"text":"we started a program that we thought\nshould be seven hours and four minutes."},{"time":177615,"text":"Actually, it turned out\nto be seven hours and 14 minutes"},{"time":180479,"text":"due to a signal failure\nat the last station."},{"time":184983,"text":"We had four cameras,"},{"time":186957,"text":"three of them pointing out\nto the beautiful nature."},{"time":190263,"text":"Some talking to the guests,\nsome information."},{"time":194233,"text":"(Video) Train announcement: \nWe will arrive at Haugastøl Station."},{"time":198283,"text":"TH: And that's about it,"},{"time":199651,"text":"but of course, also"},{"time":201446,"text":"the 160 tunnels gave us the opportunity\nto do some archives."},{"time":205287,"text":"Narrator [in Norwegian]: Then a bit of\nflirting while the food is digested."},{"time":210483,"text":"The last downhill stretch\nbefore we reach our destination."},{"time":215901,"text":"We pass Mjølfjell Station."},{"time":220207,"text":"Then a new tunnel."},{"time":222615,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":223765,"text":"TH: And now we thought, yes,\nwe have a brilliant program."},{"time":227022,"text":"It will fit for the 2,000\ntrain spotters in Norway."},{"time":231619,"text":"We brought it on air in November 2009."},{"time":234220,"text":"But no, this was far more attractive."},{"time":236667,"text":"This is the five biggest TV channels\nin Norway on a normal Friday,"},{"time":240489,"text":"and if you look at NRK2 over here,"},{"time":242788,"text":"look what happened when they put on\nthe Bergen Railway show:"},{"time":246984,"text":"1.2 million Norwegians\nwatched part of this program."},{"time":250709,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":254624,"text":"And another funny thing:"},{"time":256810,"text":"When the host on our main channel,"},{"time":258757,"text":"after they have got news for you,"},{"time":261224,"text":"she said, \"And on our second channel,"},{"time":263662,"text":"the train has now\nnearly reached Myrdal station.\""},{"time":266657,"text":"Thousands of people\njust jumped on the train"},{"time":269350,"text":"on our second channel like this.\n(Laughter)"},{"time":273366,"text":"This was also a huge success\nin terms of social media."},{"time":277012,"text":"It was so nice to see all the thousands\nof Facebook and Twitter users"},{"time":281116,"text":"discussing the same view,"},{"time":283977,"text":"talking to each other as if they were\non the same train together."},{"time":288463,"text":"And especially, I like this one.\nIt's a 76-year-old man."},{"time":291748,"text":"He's watched all the program,"},{"time":293428,"text":"and at the end station, he rises up\nto pick up what he thinks is his luggage,"},{"time":297445,"text":"and his head hit the curtain rod,"},{"time":301003,"text":"and he realized he is\nin his own living room."},{"time":303691,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":309426,"text":"So that's strong and living TV."},{"time":314070,"text":"Four hundred and thirty-six\nminute by minute on a Friday night,"},{"time":317414,"text":"and during that first night,"},{"time":319275,"text":"the first Twitter message came:\nWhy be a chicken?"},{"time":321829,"text":"Why stop at 436\nwhen you can expand that"},{"time":327498,"text":"to 8,040, minute by minute,"},{"time":331159,"text":"and do the iconic journey in Norway,"},{"time":333365,"text":"the coastal ship journey Hurtigruten\nfrom Bergen to Kirkenes,"},{"time":336807,"text":"almost 3,000 kilometers,\ncovering most of our coast."},{"time":340361,"text":"It has 120-year-old,\nvery interesting history,"},{"time":344939,"text":"and literally takes part in life\nand death along the coast."},{"time":349755,"text":"So just a week after the Bergen Railway,"},{"time":352126,"text":"we called the Hurtigruten company\nand we started planning for our next show."}]},{"cues":[{"time":358082,"text":"We wanted to do something different."},{"time":360245,"text":"The Bergen Railway was a recorded program."},{"time":363526,"text":"So when we sat in our editing room,"},{"time":365616,"text":"we watched this picture --\nit's all Ål Station --"},{"time":368220,"text":"we saw this journalist."},{"time":369728,"text":"We had called him, we had spoken to him,"},{"time":371681,"text":"and when we left the station,"},{"time":373537,"text":"he took this picture of us\nand he waved to the camera,"},{"time":376728,"text":"and we thought,"},{"time":378188,"text":"what if more people knew\nthat we were on board that train?"},{"time":381440,"text":"Would more people show up?"},{"time":383286,"text":"What would it look like?"},{"time":385259,"text":"So we decided our next project,\nit should be live."},{"time":388789,"text":"We wanted this picture of us on the fjord\nand on the screen at the same time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":395034,"text":"So this is not the first time\nNRK had been on board a ship."},{"time":398355,"text":"This is back in 1964,"},{"time":400073,"text":"when the technical managers\nhave suits and ties"},{"time":402929,"text":"and NRK rolled all its equipment\non board a ship,"},{"time":406969,"text":"and 200 meters out of the shore,\ntransmitting the signal back,"},{"time":411009,"text":"and in the machine room,\nthey talked to the machine guy,"},{"time":414957,"text":"and on the deck, they have\nsplendid entertainment."},{"time":419110,"text":"So being on a ship, \nit's not the first time."},{"time":425309,"text":"But five and a half days in a row,\nand live, we wanted some help."},{"time":430335,"text":"And we asked our viewers out there,\nwhat do you want to see?"},{"time":434498,"text":"What do you want us to film?\nHow do you want this to look?"},{"time":438610,"text":"Do you want us to make a website?\nWhat do you want on it?"},{"time":441318,"text":"And we got some answers\nfrom you out there,"},{"time":443556,"text":"and it helped us a very lot\nto build the program."},{"time":447807,"text":"So in June 2011,"},{"time":450662,"text":"23 of us went on board\nthe Hurtigruten coastal ship"},{"time":454446,"text":"and we set off."},{"time":456164,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":515373,"text":"I have some really strong memories\nfrom that week, and it's all about people."},{"time":519092,"text":"This guy, for instance,"},{"time":520732,"text":"he's head of research\nat the University in Tromsø"},{"time":523425,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":525188,"text":"And I will show you a piece of cloth,"},{"time":530071,"text":"this one."},{"time":534378,"text":"It's the other strong memory."},{"time":535922,"text":"It belongs to a guy called Erik Hansen."},{"time":540796,"text":"And it's people like those two\nwho took a firm grip of our program,"},{"time":548818,"text":"and together with thousands\nof others along the route,"},{"time":552639,"text":"they made the program what it became."},{"time":555519,"text":"They made all the stories."},{"time":558047,"text":"This is Karl. He's in the ninth grade."},{"time":561091,"text":"It says, \"I will be a little\nlate for school tomorrow.\""},{"time":564713,"text":"He was supposed to be\nin the school at 8 a.m."},{"time":567383,"text":"He came at 9 a.m., and he didn't\nget a note from his teacher,"},{"time":570484,"text":"because the teacher\nhad watched the program."},{"time":572585,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":574046,"text":"How did we do this?"},{"time":575719,"text":"Yes, we took a conference room\non board the Hurtigruten."},{"time":578935,"text":"We turned it into\na complete TV control room."},{"time":582047,"text":"We made it all work, of course,"},{"time":585100,"text":"and then we took along 11 cameras."},{"time":587259,"text":"This is one of them."},{"time":588374,"text":"This is my sketch from February,"},{"time":590347,"text":"and when you give this sketch\nto professional people"},{"time":592855,"text":"in the Norwegian broadcasting company NRK,"},{"time":595084,"text":"you get some cool stuff back."},{"time":598024,"text":"And with some very creative solutions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":602201,"text":"(Video) Narrator [in Norwegian]: \nRun it up and down."},{"time":604719,"text":"This is Norway's most\nimportant drill right now."},{"time":608141,"text":"It regulates the height of a bow\ncamera in NRK's live production,"},{"time":614054,"text":"one of 11 that capture\ngreat shots from the MS Nord-Norge."},{"time":618790,"text":"Eight wires keep the camera stable."},{"time":621461,"text":"Cameraman: I work \non different camera solutions."},{"time":625106,"text":"They're just tools\nused in a different context."}]},{"cues":[{"time":628960,"text":"TH: Another camera is this one.\nIt's normally used for sports."},{"time":632304,"text":"It made it possible for us to take\nclose-up pictures of people"},{"time":635903,"text":"100 kilomteres away,"},{"time":637923,"text":"like this one. (Laughter)"},{"time":642358,"text":"People called us and asked,\nhow is this man doing?"},{"time":645190,"text":"He's doing fine. Everything went well."},{"time":648139,"text":"We also could take pictures of\npeople waving at us,"},{"time":651372,"text":"people along the route,\nthousands of them,"},{"time":653689,"text":"and they all had a phone in their hand."},{"time":656114,"text":"And when you take a picture of them,\nand they get the message,"},{"time":659099,"text":"\"Now we are on TV, dad,\"\nthey start waving back."},{"time":661954,"text":"This was waving TV \nfor five and a half days,"},{"time":664114,"text":"and people get so extremely happy"},{"time":666273,"text":"when they can send a warm message\nto their loved ones."}]},{"cues":[{"time":671090,"text":"It was also a great success\non social media."},{"time":674609,"text":"On the last day, we met\nHer Majesty the Queen of Norway,"},{"time":677418,"text":"and Twitter couldn't quite handle it."},{"time":681017,"text":"And we also, on the web,"},{"time":683386,"text":"during this week we streamed\nmore than 100 years of video"},{"time":688260,"text":"to 148 nations,"},{"time":691628,"text":"and the websites are still there\nand they will be forever, actually,"},{"time":695829,"text":"because Hurtigruten was selected"},{"time":697735,"text":"to be part of the Norwegian\nUNESCO list of documents,"},{"time":702267,"text":"and it's also in\nthe Guinness Book of Records"},{"time":705258,"text":"as the longest documentary ever."},{"time":708764,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":712247,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":715985,"text":"But it's a long program,"},{"time":719375,"text":"so some watched part of it,\nlike the Prime Minister."},{"time":722463,"text":"Some watched a little bit more."},{"time":724205,"text":"It says, \"I haven't used\nmy bed for five days.\""},{"time":728614,"text":"And he's 82 years old,\nand he hardly slept."},{"time":733085,"text":"He kept watching because\nsomething might happen,"},{"time":736441,"text":"though it probably won't. (Laughter)"},{"time":738854,"text":"This is the number\nof viewers along the route."},{"time":741503,"text":"You can see the famous Trollfjord"},{"time":743105,"text":"and a day after, all-time high for NRK2."},{"time":747849,"text":"If you see the four biggest\nchannels in Norway during June 2011,"},{"time":753671,"text":"they will look like this,"},{"time":755968,"text":"and as a TV producer, it's a pleasure\nto put Hurtigruten on top of it."},{"time":759818,"text":"It looks like this:"},{"time":761541,"text":"3.2 million Norwegians\nwatched part of this program,"},{"time":764908,"text":"and we are only five million here."},{"time":766788,"text":"Even the passengers on board\nthe Hurtigruten coastal ship --"},{"time":769822,"text":"(Laughter) --"},{"time":771436,"text":"they chose to watched the telly\ninstead of turning 90 degrees"},{"time":775561,"text":"and watching out the window."}]},{"cues":[{"time":778435,"text":"So we were allowed to be \npart of people's living room"},{"time":781416,"text":"with this strange TV program,"},{"time":784173,"text":"with music, nature, people."},{"time":787546,"text":"And Slow TV was now a buzzword,"},{"time":790239,"text":"and we started looking for other things\nwe could make Slow TV about."},{"time":794073,"text":"So we could either take something long\nand make it a topic,"},{"time":797515,"text":"like with the railway and the Hurtigruten,"},{"time":799736,"text":"or we could take a topic and make it long."},{"time":802267,"text":"This is the last project.\nIt's the peep show."},{"time":804775,"text":"It's 14 hours of birdwatching\non a TV screen,"},{"time":807561,"text":"actually 87 days on the web."},{"time":810742,"text":"We have made 18 hours\nof live salmon fishing."},{"time":814364,"text":"It actually took three hours\nbefore we got the first fish,"},{"time":817429,"text":"and that's quite slow."},{"time":819240,"text":"We have made 12 hours of boat ride\ninto the beautiful Telemark Canal,"},{"time":824276,"text":"and we have made another train ride\nwith the northern railway,"},{"time":827821,"text":"and because this we couldn't do live,\nwe did it in four seasons"},{"time":831823,"text":"just to give the viewer\nanother experience on the way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":837058,"text":"So our next project got us\nsome attention outside Norway."},{"time":841598,"text":"This is from the Colbert Report\non Comedy Central."}]},{"cues":[{"time":844484,"text":"(Video) Stephen Colbert: I've got my eye\non a wildly popular program from Norway"},{"time":848280,"text":"called \"National Firewood Night,\""},{"time":851213,"text":"which consisted of mostly people in parkas\nchatting and chopping in the woods,"},{"time":855485,"text":"and then eight hours of a fire \nburning in a fireplace. (Laughter)"},{"time":859130,"text":"It destroyed the other \ntop Norwegian shows,"},{"time":861731,"text":"like \"So You Think\nYou Can Watch Paint Dry\""},{"time":864146,"text":"and \"The Amazing Glacier Race.\""},{"time":867977,"text":"And get this, almost 20 percent\nof the Norwegian population tuned in,"},{"time":873182,"text":"20 percent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":874850,"text":"TH: So, when wood fire and wood chopping\ncan be that interesting,"},{"time":878727,"text":"why not knitting?"},{"time":880260,"text":"So on our next project,"},{"time":881978,"text":"we used more than eight hours\nto go live from a sheep to a sweater,"},{"time":886995,"text":"and Jimmy Kimmel in the ABC show,"},{"time":889302,"text":"he liked that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":891451,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":898324,"text":"(Video) Jimmy Kimmel: Even the people\non the show are falling asleep,"},{"time":902044,"text":"and after all that,\nthe knitters actually failed"},{"time":904320,"text":"to break the world record."},{"time":905996,"text":"They did not succeed,"},{"time":907342,"text":"but remember the old Norwegian saying,"},{"time":909585,"text":"it's not whether you win\nor lose that counts."},{"time":911763,"text":"In fact, nothing counts, \nand death is coming for us all."},{"time":914487,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":915931,"text":"TH: Exactly. So why does this stand out?"},{"time":918825,"text":"This is so completely different\nto other TV programming."},{"time":922105,"text":"We take the viewer on a journey\nthat happens right now in real time,"},{"time":926847,"text":"and the viewer gets the feeling\nof actually being there,"},{"time":930424,"text":"actually being on the train, on the boat,"},{"time":932588,"text":"and knitting together with others,"},{"time":934415,"text":"and the reason I think\nwhy they're doing that"},{"time":936872,"text":"is because we don't edit the timeline."},{"time":939352,"text":"It's important that\nwe don't edit the timeline,"},{"time":941720,"text":"and it's also important\nthat what we make Slow TV about"},{"time":944919,"text":"is something that we all can relate to,\nthat the viewer can relate to,"},{"time":949648,"text":"and that somehow has \na root in our culture."},{"time":952765,"text":"This is a picture from last summer"},{"time":954491,"text":"when we traveled the coast\nagain for seven weeks."},{"time":957068,"text":"And of course this is a lot of planning,\nthis is a lot of logistics."},{"time":961431,"text":"So this is the working plan\nfor 150 people last summer,"},{"time":965543,"text":"but more important is what you don't plan."},{"time":968388,"text":"You don't plan what's going to happen."},{"time":970905,"text":"You have to just\ntake your cameras with you."},{"time":973891,"text":"It's like a sports event."},{"time":975411,"text":"You rig them and you see what's happening."},{"time":977570,"text":"So this is actually\nthe whole running order"},{"time":980054,"text":"for Hurtigruten, 134 hours,\njust written on one page."},{"time":984501,"text":"We didn't know anything more\nwhen we left Bergen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":988553,"text":"So you have to let the viewers\nmake the stories themselves,"},{"time":991897,"text":"and I'll give you an example of that."},{"time":994126,"text":"This is from last summer,"},{"time":995890,"text":"and as a TV producer,"},{"time":997748,"text":"it's a nice picture, but now\nyou can cut to the next one."},{"time":1001395,"text":"But this is Slow TV,"},{"time":1003135,"text":"so you have to keep this picture until \nit really starts hurting your stomach,"},{"time":1006809,"text":"and then you keep it a little bit longer,"},{"time":1009169,"text":"and when you keep it that long,"},{"time":1010689,"text":"I'm sure some of you now\nhave noticed the cow."},{"time":1013453,"text":"Some of you have seen the flag."},{"time":1015487,"text":"Some of you start wondering,\nis the farmer at home?"},{"time":1017893,"text":"Has he left? Is he watching the cow?"},{"time":1020340,"text":"And where is that cow going?"},{"time":1023567,"text":"So my point is, the longer\nyou keep a picture like this,"},{"time":1026801,"text":"and we kept it for 10 minutes,"},{"time":1029093,"text":"you start making\nthe stories in your own head."},{"time":1033064,"text":"That's Slow TV."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1037267,"text":"So we think that Slow TV is\none nice way of telling a TV story,"},{"time":1042677,"text":"and we think that we\ncan continue doing it,"},{"time":1045161,"text":"not too often, once or twice a year,\nso we keep the feeling of an event,"},{"time":1049665,"text":"and we also think that\nthe good Slow TV idea,"},{"time":1052568,"text":"that's the idea when people say,"},{"time":1054240,"text":"\"Oh no, you can't put that on TV.\""},{"time":1057676,"text":"When people smile, it might be\na very good slow idea,"},{"time":1060718,"text":"so after all, life is best\nwhen it's a bit strange."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1064970,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1066463,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}